description: This match doesn’t even seem fair. Alexa Nova is a petite all natural redhead with some very powerful legs and some wrestling experience. Todd Jones is a Tall Dark and handsome beef cake with no wrestling experience whatsoever. See what we mean when we say it doesn’t seem fair…..todd jones who has never fought a day in his life stand no chance against Alexa Nova. This match is the quintessential display of how powerful skill is over size and strength. We can’t be too mean to Todd. Getting beat by a little 5’3 chick would be too humiliating. The ref gives Todd some tips, it’s up to todd to be a good student and listen. Todd picks up some moves along the way. This is a unique experience for the fans to see a fighter progress right in front of their eyes. Todd is able to win at least one round but he is behind big time going into round 2. Does Todd have enough to squeak by with a victory? Alexa is impressed with Todd’s performance so she does insist that he fucks her in the ass win lose or draw.
title:
Petite Redhead Female Dominates the Big Stud in
Wrestling Match
